<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Economics Professor Named Inaugural Richard T. Crotty Endowed Chair</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Joanne Chive
		
		<span class="date">Sept. 15, 2008</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 226px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="http://news.ucf.edu/resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1550/en_US/harrison main crop.jpg" height="345" width="226"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Courtesy of the College of Business Administration</p>
			
			<p>Professor Glenn W. Harrison will teach and conduct research in urban and regional economics.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041023eeeb10011c665a1e800075b3">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
